                            <comment id="13699518" author="ekoifman" created="Wed, 3 Jul 2013 22:14:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-4808&quot; title=&quot;WebHCat job submission is killed by TaskTracker since it&amp;#39;s not sending a heartbeat properly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HIVE-4808&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HIVE-4808&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.patch has the diffs.&lt;br/&gt;
